- A completed transcription is assumed to have a status ID of 2; 
- Average quality scores include accuracy, fluency, coherence, and overall score for each transcriber's work; 
- The most recent transcription is determined by the transcription date; 
- Comments are associated with the media and counted for the most recent transcription.

